description.narrative: This activity (TEP programme office management costs) is a component of Transforming Education in Pakistan reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £11,935,832. This component benefits Pakistan, and works in the following sector(s): Education policy and administrative management, Educational research, Primary education, Secondary education. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited, DAI Europe, Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office. The start date is 13-05-2011 and the end date is 31-08-2018.
